    About this item

    • Right Angle USB C: UGREEN USB-C cable with an innovative 90 degrees L design. It's more convenient and more comfortable for playing games, watching videos, reading e-books when you lie on the couch or bed while charging.
    • Safe and Quick Charge: This USB C to USB A cable supports Quick Charge 2.0 and 3.0, with max output up to 3A. It is fully compatible with Samsung Adaptive Fast Charging AFC and Huawei Fast Charging Protocol FCP, providing 5V 3A, 9V 2A or 12V 1.5A fast charge. With a built-in 56KΩ resistor, this type c charger guarantees reliable conductivity and charging, protecting your cell phones from damage due to excessive current.
    • Broad Compatibility: This type c charging cable is compatible with Samsung S20 S10 S10e S10 Plus Galaxy S9 S8 Plus Note 9 Note8 A8 2018, Galaxy Tab S3 9.7, Galaxy Fold, iPad Pro 11, 2018 iPad Pro 12.9, LG G5 G6 G7 G8 ThinQ, LG V20 V30 V40 V50, Motorola Razr 2019, Moto G7 G6, Moto Z force, Moto z2 play, Nintendo switch, compatible with GoPro Hero 5 hero 6 7 black, HTC 10 U12+, OnePlus 2, Huawei P9. IMPORTANT NOTE: This right angle c cable can NOT work with phone case thicker than 2mm.
    • Fast Data Transfer: Triple-shielding provides better protection against interference, ensuring fast and stable data transmission. This USB C to USB A 2.0 cable guarantees data transfer up to 480 Mbps.
    • Resistant and Durable: Aluminum housing allows you to feel the elegance of the metal and increase its service life, much more resistant to wear and corrosion. 5X durable nylon braided cable not only stay tangling-free but also flexible enough to be wrapped up and put in a bag. Up to 10,000+ bend and 10,000+ plugging and unplugging test ensure this cord a longer lifespan.

    Product Description

    Fast Charging Cable

    UGREEN USB type C cable supports Quick Charge 2.0, QC 3.0 and Samsung AFC fast charging, with the output up to 18W max: 5V 3A, 9V 2A or 12V 1.5A. It can provide full charging speed with your original QC USB-C power charger, as fast as the original cable.

    Safe and Reliable

    This USB C charging cable fully complies with USB-C fast charge protocol and a built-in 56KΩ pull-up resistor, upgraded intelligent chip with multi protections inside. It provides reliable conductivity and stable charging current, protecting your smartphones from damage due to over-current or over-voltage.

    Fast Data Syncing

    For data transmission, this USB-C to USB A 2.0 fast charging cord supports syncing speed up to 480 Mbps.

    90 Degree Right Angle USB C to USB A Charger

    With an innovative 90 degrees L design, UGREEN USB-C cable is designed to reduce wear and tear on the cable and on your Type-C smartphones especially ideal for limited space. It's more convenient and more comfortable for playing games, watching videos, reading e-books when you lie on the couch or bed while charging.

    Widely Compatibility

    Please note this right angle USB C cable CAN'T be used with Otterbox phone case or any phone case thicker than 2.5 mm

    Compatible for Samsung Galaxy S10 S10e S10 Plus, Galaxy S9 S9 Plus, Galaxy S8 S8+ Note 9 8, Samsung Galaxy Tab S3 9.7, Samsung Galaxy Fold

    Compatible for Apple iPad Pro 11, iPad Pro 12.9 2018

    Compatible for LG G5 G6 G7 ThinQ, LG V20 V30 V40 V50 ThinQ

    Compatible for Motorola Moto G6, Moto z, z force, z play, Moto z2 force z2 play

    Compatible for Nintendo Switch console, Lenovo Zuk Z1, Nokia N1, ZTE Axon 7

    Compatible for GoPro Hero 5, hero 7 black hero 7 white hero 7 silver, hero 6 black, gopro hero 2018

    Compatible for Microsoft Lumia 950, Lumia 950XL, HTC 10 U12+, Huawei P9 Plus, Huawei P9, OnePlus 2

    Partially Compatible Devices as Below

    Note: Due to limited Max 3A current, this Type C charger cannot charge the following smartphones at its full speed.

    Partially compatible for OnePlus 3 3T 5 5t 6 6t 7 pro, google pixel 2 3 , Pixel XL , pixel 3 xl, Pixel 2 XL, Nexus 5X 6P.

    Enhanced Durability

    Aluminum housing allows you to feel the elegance of the metal and increase its service life, much more resistant to wear and corrosion.

    5X durable nylon braided cable not only stay tangling-free but also flexible enough to be wrapped up and put in a bag.

    Up to 10,000+ bend and 10,000+ plugging and unplugging test ensure this cord a longer lifespan.

I can charge my Switch in the case, but the charging cable that it comes with is straight, so the rim of the case puts pressure on the end of the cable and, in turn, the Switch's port.         Prior to purchasing this UGREEN model, I tried an ANLOER cable, which can be found here:

        I found that playing Dragon Quest Builders 2 drained the battery faster than the cable could charge it. I swapped that cable for this one, and it charged to 100% and stayed there during use. The angled USB C port on this UGREEN cable is also much smaller than the ANLOER cable.

        This UGREEN cable works perfectly at charging my Switch fast, and the angled end is the perfect fit for charging inside the case. Overall, I didn't find any flaws with the product and highly recommend it. 5/5 stars
